description: I was so exhausted and about to crush into the bed but suddenly my phone rang. As always, somebody in need of money. We talked about his debts in his apartment. His place was empty, smelly and kinda hostile. But I wasn´t there to evaluate his apartment but to fuck his straight, virgin ass! I offered him a solution, after some thinking he finally accepted. All the action had to be on the table cause there was nothing like a sofa. While sucking, I mentioned that I wanna fuck him.
title: Debt Dandy 73
